# Design Guidelines

Brand personality: **trustworthy, warm, refined.** Elegant minimalism — prestigious enough to feel expert, warm enough to feel human.

## Palette

- Navy `#1E2E45` — authority, headings, primary surfaces
- Gold `#B19460` — warmth, accents, hover/focus states, icons
- Cream `#e8e9e1` — background, ground tone
- Never pure black (#000) or pure white (#fff)

## Typography

- **Headings/buttons:** DM Serif Display (`dm_serif`)
- **Body/nav:** DM Sans (`dm_sans`), font-weight 200 for body
- **Hero subtitle:** Encode Sans (`encode`)
- Use CSS clamp vars (`--fs-xl`, `--fs-l`, `--fs-m`) for responsive sizing

## Animation

- Scroll-triggered reveals via `<Animated>` component (react-spring)
- Easing: `ease-out-quart` (cubic-bezier(0.25, 1, 0.5, 1)) — smooth deceleration
- Hover: subtle lift (`-translate-y-0.5`) + shadow. Active: press down (`translate-y-px`)
- Always respect `prefers-reduced-motion`
- Never use bounce or elastic easing

## Do NOT

- Add playful animations, whimsical copy, or bouncy easing
- Use glassmorphism, gradient text, neon accents, or dark-mode-by-default
- Introduce colors outside navy/gold/cream without discussion
- Use generic AI aesthetics (purple gradients, Inter font, card-heavy layouts)
- Hardcode visible text — use `next-intl` translation keys
